{{ref improve|date=October 2016}} {{Infobox magazine | image_file = | image_size = | image_caption = | editor = Patricia Anderson | editor_title = Editor | previous_editor = | staff_writer = | frequency = Quarterly | circulation = | category = [[Fine art]]s | company = | publisher = Westwick-Farrow Pty Ltd | firstdate = March–June 2003 | country = [[Australia]] | based = [[Sydney]] | language = English | website = {{url|www.artreview.com.au}} | issn = 1447-8587 }} '''''Australian Art Review''''' is an integrated quarterly magazine and website based in [[Sydney]],<ref>{{cite web|title=Australian Art Publishing Pty Ltd|url=http://www.latestdatabase.com/business-directory/australian-art-publishing-pty-ltd/|work=Latest Database|accessdate=29 October 2016}}</ref> featuring a mixture of exhibition reviews, artist and gallery profiles, advice for collectors and articles by art critics and scholars.
==History== The first edition of the ''Australian Art Review'' appeared in March/June 2003. In 2008, the magazine was purchased by Westwick-Farrow Media. {{clear}}
